{"tid":2245371,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[原神有感] 遊戲業界即將崩壞 (2)","createTime":"2020-10-16T07:30:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-17T07:24:43.000Z","uid":188922,"like":7,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"56757c58ef7208a36a7e1bc60fcf8e29227a08ce","tid":2245371,"uid":188922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T07:30:21.000Z","msg":"開心見到咁多人認真討論  原來都唔小人對遊戲業咁多睇法  唔係個個盲目撚<br />\n補充幾個點  <br />\n-好多人集火電話game, 我所講嘅有d唔同，係crossplatform,  可能之後出隻console game都會順便加埋手機版吸金。<br />\n<br />\n-我自己都會玩手機game同課金， 我覺得佢值幾錢， 我就課幾多。 e.g. rdr2賣緊458, 我玩fgo頂多課200算，唔值<br />\n<br />\n-有d論點成日話 「乜野叫抄？拳皇夠抄街霸啦， 仲有神抄呢」 呢個值得探討，我覺得原神最抄個位係抄左人最signature嘅美術風格， 但又加左d嘔心元素落去。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原post<br />\n「原神有感」遊戲業界即將崩壞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2243979\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2243979</a>"},{"pid":"c0a71f7c662d9db49d5f759193c74f08bc7bbd9d","tid":2245371,"uid":349563,"like":14,"dislike":3,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T07:56:12.000Z","msg":"唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />廠商辛辛苦苦用幾年時間整隻3A 大作 <br />\n都不及一隻垃圾手機game 一個season 既課金量"},{"pid":"f7291fab013c9517c3ec780523104feffe5e9765","tid":2245371,"uid":183085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T08:03:34.000Z","msg":"Fgo每年買福袋就算"},{"pid":"2e31f5f028e0605b8c6f6149172113007b9bbc8c","tid":2245371,"uid":229185,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T08:04:03.000Z","msg":"好多鬼玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd1de127b062d3c3715b6ca2b7e26ad6cebd94c2","tid":2245371,"uid":158645,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T08:11:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />廠商辛辛苦苦用幾年時間整隻3A 大作 <br />\n都不及一隻垃圾手機game <span class=\"red\">一日</span> 既課金量</blockquote>"},{"pid":"b7ed2102a1d0daa326d26e49c1d53a3e97ede152","tid":2245371,"uid":11055,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T08:13:33.000Z","msg":"其實抽蛋買skin呢啲真係毒瘤黎<br />\n對game 廠而言，我畫兩張圖搵得多過開發隻3A出黎，<br />\n點解要吃力不討好？<br />\n3A唔一定好賣架喎，會出事架喎，<br />\n但係抽蛋，呢水唔好賣咪出下一水囉，<br />\n邊個time cost 大啲？<br />\n對玩家而言，抽蛋換皮驚越來越多，<br />\n真正有內涵有深度嘅驚就越來越少，<br />\n唔好笑人咩打機講深度，講內涵，<br />\nWitcher,DS,以前既FF,TLOU都有佢地想帶出嘅意思，<br />\n亦都豐富左好多人既內心。<br />\n但偏偏收最多錢嘅就係啲換皮驚，<br />\n咁以後仲邊有驚廠肯花成本去整新野？<br />\n睇下fifa 2k呢啲運動類game已經開始進入換皮死胡同啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66cb8195bbf399715c5d4b2d48e2ef33d7cf505e","tid":2245371,"uid":345443,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T09:47:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9m47j1z-LB8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9m47j1z-LB8&d=Z58AETknIeTPCCdXMCOVU5mjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=45798161\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9m47j1z-LB8</a><br />\n呢條片講得好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你係可以搵好多excuse話隻game唔同, <br />\n話呢隻係有adventure成份既rpg 有別於botw主要係adventure game blah blah blah<br />\n隻game本身可能都唔係差<br />\n但成隻game個底係一樣照盤過去"},{"pid":"552be66b15747391fc858d3a0d8694c2ee944f53","tid":2245371,"uid":345443,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T09:57:18.000Z","msg":"當年鬼佬overwatch迷猛屌paladins, <br />\n宜家有隻真係抄既冇人鬧<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d17cb28e47b2d4ba82928b2494e7370d538882e","tid":2245371,"uid":37697,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"552be66b15747391fc858d3a0d8694c2ee944f53","tid":2245371,"uid":345443,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T09:57:18.000Z","msg":"當年鬼佬overwatch迷猛屌paladins, <br />\n宜家有隻真係抄既冇人鬧<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"cit